    • Field Detail

      • key

        public String key
        The Channel identifier key

      • timer

        public String timer
        The user-defined timer in case the Channel is automatically triggered. If the user did not specify a value, the default is used. If the Channel is of input type or not automatic, this property is null.

      • properties

        public Map<String,Object> properties
        The user-binded properties in the form of an associative array of key/value pairs. If the user did not specify bindings and there is a direct match in the input message, that property is used. If the user did not specify bindings and there is not any other match, the value is null. If the Channel is of type output or has no properties for binding, then this property is an empty array.
